description:
GBR will play various Husker songs and sound clips.

Full list of supported sound clips:
Fight Song (There is No Place Like Nebraska)
Hail Varsity
Tunnel Walk
Touchdown Tommie Frazier
Johnny 'The Jet' Rodgers
